name: Experiment Or Die #105
description: Been creating a collage every day for a year and though the goal has not changed the concept and structure of the collection has evolved and is ever changing. It's kind of like survival of the fittest out here as an artist. Learn to excel and survive. Find your community and be ready and willing to adapt and pivot at any time, or you might just get left behind with the dust and bones. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
